          <h6 style="background-color: red;width: 280px;margin: 12% 0px 0px 50px;font-size: 25px;color: white;">&nbsp;FLOW GLOBAL LIMITED</h6>
          <h1 class="privacy_tittle" style="color: red;"><b>DATA PRIVACY & PROTECTION POLICY</b></h1>
      </div>
